OL,3,C'Absolutely reckless' to give murderer
OL,4,Ccompassionate release, family warns
OL,6,FThe family of a mother-of-three
OL,7,Fmurdered 28 years ago have criticised
OL,8,Fdiscussions about her killer's
OL,9,Fpotential early release from prison as
OL,10,F"absolutely reckless".
OL,12,FVictor Farrant was handed a whole life
OL,13,Fsentence for the murder of his ex-
OL,14,Fgirlfriend Glenda Hoskins, who was in
OL,15,Fher forties, in Portsmouth in February
OL,16,F1996.
OL,18,FBut now her grieving children have
OL,19,Fbeen told Farrant is ill and can no
OL,20,Flonger receive care in jail.
