OL,3,C'Absolutely reckless' to give murderer
OL,4,Ccompassionate release, family warns
OL,6,FGlenda's eldest son Iain says his
OL,7,Fmother's killer is a dangerous man who
OL,8,Fcould "strike again" if freed from
OL,9,Fjail.
OL,11,FThe 47-year-old said his family felt
OL,12,F"railroaded" after they were contacted
OL,13,Fby officials last Monday to discuss
OL,14,Fgeographical exclusion zones for
OL,15,FFarrant in the event he was released
OL,16,Fon compassionate grounds.
OL,18,FThe family were told the convict has
OL,19,Fterminal cancer and could have months
OL,20,Fto live, but Mr Hoskins said the
OL,21,Ffamily objects to his release.
