OL,3,C'Absolutely reckless' to give murderer
OL,4,Ccompassionate release, family warns
OL,6,FThe restaurateur, based in Liverpool,
OL,7,Fdescribed Farrant as a "completely
OL,8,Fdangerous man", adding he knows how to
OL,9,Fmilk the system and would stop at
OL,10,Fnothing to get out of prison.
OL,12,FThe Ministry of Justice (MoJ) said it
OL,13,Fhas not yet received a formal release
OL,14,Fapplication.
OL,16,F"For anybody that's got any say in
OL,17,Fconsidering this, it's a completely
OL,18,Freckless decision to make," Mr Hoskins
OL,19,Fsaid.
