OL,4,Ccompassionate release, family warns
OL,6,FFarrant was jailed for life for the
OL,7,Fmurder of his former girlfriend Mrs
OL,8,FHoskins, then aged in her forties, and
OL,9,Fthe attempted murder of Ann Fidler,
OL,10,F45, at Winchester Crown Court in 1998.
OL,12,FSentencing him, Mr Justice Butterfield
OL,13,Fhad said: "This murder was so terrible
OL,14,Fand you are so dangerous that in your
OL,15,Fcase the sentence of life should mean
OL,16,Fjust that.
OL,18,F"You should never be released."
