OL,4,Ccompassionate release, family warns
OL,6,FFarrant had been jailed in November
OL,7,F1988 for a total of 12 years for rape
OL,8,Fand other offences.
OL,10,FHe was released on 7 November 1995,
OL,11,Fjust weeks before he savagely beat Ms
OL,12,FFidler at her home in Eastleigh,
OL,13,FHampshire.
OL,15,FSix weeks later, he murdered Mrs
OL,16,FHoskins at her home in Portsmouth by
OL,17,Fpushing her under the water in the
OL,18,Fbath.
