OL,3,C'Absolutely reckless' to give murderer
OL,4,Ccompassionate release, family warns
OL,6,FHe left her body in the attic, where
OL,7,Fit was later discovered by her 15-year-
OL,8,Fold daughter Katie.
OL,10,FAfter killing Mrs Hoskins, Farrant
OL,11,Fwent on the run and was eventually
OL,12,Ffound in the south of France.
OL,14,FMr Hoskins questioned how Farrant
OL,15,Fwould be policed if he was granted
OL,16,Fcompassionate release, and said the
OL,17,Ffamily have not been given details
OL,18,Fabout whether he would be staying at a
OL,19,Fhospice under supervision or other
OL,20,Faccommodation.
