OL,3,C'Absolutely reckless' to give murderer
OL,4,Ccompassionate release, family warns
OL,6,FSpeaking of his siblings' reaction, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "They obviously feel petrified
OL,8,Fof this and again, we never, ever saw
OL,9,Fthis coming because the judge's
OL,10,Fcomments was he should serve life and
OL,11,Fhe will serve life.
OL,13,F"The fact that he may or may not be
OL,14,Fdying doesn't give us any comfort
OL,15,Fwhatsoever. If someone's got nothing
OL,16,Fto lose... I think well, what's to
OL,17,Fstop him from killing or raping or
OL,18,Fkidnapping again?"
