OL,3,C'Absolutely reckless' to give murderer
OL,4,Ccompassionate release, family warns
OL,6,FThe family have written to their MPs,
OL,7,Fto Home Secretary James Cleverly and
OL,8,FJustice Secretary Alex Chalk
OL,9,Fexpressing their objections to
OL,10,FFarrant's release.
OL,12,FThey said a panel meeting discussing
OL,13,FFarrant's release is being held in
OL,14,Fearly April before it will go to the
OL,15,FMinistry of Justice.
OL,17,FThe power lies with the Justice
OL,18,FSecretary to grant or deny
OL,19,Fapplications for early release from
OL,20,Fprison.
